       Lower liblzma dep to latest stable (5.0.5) instead of dev (5.1.0)
       Set NoDisplay=true for Disk Image writer and Disk Image Mounter apps
       Bump version to 3.10.0
       Update NEWS for release

 Seán de Búrca (1):
       Fix autogen and configure

