Cosimo Cecchi (4):
      Add a --format-device command line option
      Resolve backing crypto device when selecting object
      utils: move code to ensure unused volume to gduutils.c
      Add a --xid command line option for the format dialog

David Zeuthen (13):
      Post-release update to version 3.7.2
      Only show eject button if drive has removable media
      Don't use deprecated gtk_style_context_notify_state_change() function
      GduVolumeGrid: properly reset flags
      Add a TODO file
      Add "Historical SMART data" to TODO list
      Add TODO item for LUKS recovery key
      Convey free space for mounted volumes
      Don't warn if statvfs(3) fails
      Bump udisks2 required version to 2.0.91
      Add HighContrast to subdirs
      Document the --format-device and --xid options for gnome-disks(1)
      Update NEWS for release

